&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Manoj is standing on 11&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; position from front&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Shahin is standing on 7&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; position from back&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total of 30 people are standing in the queue facing north.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to the given information, a diagram is shown below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/07/F1_Vinanti_SSC_27.07.23_D01.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 401px; height: 115px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Number of people standing after Manoj&amp;nbsp;= 30 - 11 = 19&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Number of people between&amp;nbsp;Shahin and Manoj&amp;nbsp;= 19 - 7 = 12&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Neeraj is standing exactly in front of Shahin&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;so including one position = 12 - 1 = 11&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the number of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;people standing between Neeraj and Manoj&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;11&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Persons : &lt;/strong&gt;P, Q, N, H and S&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;P is taller than S.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;_ &amp;gt; _ &amp;gt; _ &amp;gt; P &amp;gt; S&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;N is taller than P and&amp;nbsp;S is shorter than N.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;_ &amp;gt; _ &amp;gt; N &amp;gt; P &amp;gt; S&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3)&amp;nbsp;Q is taller than N but shorter than H.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;H &amp;gt; Q &amp;gt; &lt;strong&gt;N&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;gt; P &amp;gt; S&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence,&lt;strong&gt; N&lt;/strong&gt; is the &lt;strong&gt;correct answer.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

